        <content type="html" xml:base="https://www.liyupoetry.com/1995hanxuema/啊-中亚细亚新大陆/na-hui-huang-jian-shi-yi-ding-huan-zai-fei-chi/">&lt;h3 id=&quot;na-hui-huang-jian-shi-yi-ding-huan-zai-fei-chi&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;anchor&quot; href=&quot;#na-hui-huang-jian-shi-yi-ding-huan-zai-fei-chi&quot;&gt;
    &lt;svg height=&quot;22&quot; viewbox=&quot;0 0 24 24&quot; width=&quot;22&quot; xmlns=&quot;http:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.w3.org&#x2F;2000&#x2F;svg&quot;&gt;
        &lt;path d=&quot;M0 0h24v24H0z&quot; fill=&quot;none&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;path&gt;
        &lt;path d=&quot;M3.9 12c0-1.71 1.39-3.1 3.1-3.1h4V7H7c-2.76.0-5 2.24-5 5s2.24 5 5 5h4v-1.9H7c-1.71.0-3.1-1.39-3.1-3.1zM8 13h8v-2H8v2zm9-6h-4v1.9h4c1.71.0 3.1 1.39 3.1 3.1s-1.39 3.1-3.1 3.1h-4V17h4c2.76.0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5z&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;path&gt;
    &lt;&#x2F;svg&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;那辉煌箭矢一定还在飞驰&lt;&#x2F;h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;　　　　投射到辽远西方&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;血红残阳就要逝去&lt;br &#x2F;&gt;
金黑夜幕就要降临&lt;br &#x2F;&gt;
张骞驱赶牧放的羊群归来了&lt;br &#x2F;&gt;
苍凉牧歌和着悲鸣的胡笳&lt;br &#x2F;&gt;
穿过晚秋夕照的雾霭&lt;br &#x2F;&gt;
远方毡房那缕炊烟袅袅升起&lt;br &#x2F;&gt;
像汉中故乡的金黑牡丹&lt;br &#x2F;&gt;
缓缓开放西域天幕&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;回头望着遥远西方那片金黑的云&lt;br &#x2F;&gt;
羊群浪涛般在马下汹涌&lt;br &#x2F;&gt;
啊，辉煌落日呀&lt;br &#x2F;&gt;
已经滚落&lt;br &#x2F;&gt;
金黑的地平线那边去了&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;可是那辉煌箭矢一定还在飞驰&lt;br &#x2F;&gt;
投射到辽远西方&lt;br &#x2F;&gt;
投射到辽远前方&lt;br &#x2F;&gt;
投射到辽远日夜思盼的&lt;br &#x2F;&gt;
大月氏的广袤原野&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
